olution</h2>		\n		<p>we revolutionize IT infrastructure with tailored open source solutions</p>		\n			<h2>BUILD USING OPENSOURCE\n</h2>		\n			<h4>What is Open Source?</h4>		\n		<p>Open Source from a business perspective offers several advantages:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Collaboratively developed software with openly accessible source code, encouraging innovation and community-driven improvements</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Open source software typically incurs no licensing fees, reducing financial burdens for users and organizations&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Open source software often benefits from rigorous community testing and contributions, leading to robust, reliable, and continuously improved solutions</p>\n</li>\n</ul>		\n			<h4>Why Open Source?\n</h4>		\n		<p>Monitor and track data issues with ease using our intuitive and efficient issue tracking system. Stay ahead of potential problems and improve your workflow. </p><ul><li>No license cost: Open source software incurs zero licensing fees, reducing financial burdens for users and organizations.</li><li> No maintenance effort: Open source projects are maintained by a dedicated community of developers, alleviating users from the need to handle maintenance tasks.</li><li> No risk of quality: Open source software undergoes extensive testing by a diverse community of users and companies, ensuring high-quality and reliable solutions.</li></ul>		\n			<h2>Core Solutions</h2>		\n		<p>OTechAdvisor meticulously validates and tailors each core solution to deliver unparalleled performance and security across all projects.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"334\" height=\"151\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/telechargement-10-1.webp\" alt=\"managed Services\" /></figure><h3>Trusted Cloud</h3><p>Our cloud meets the highest standards <br>of security, performance, and sovereignty<br> in the European market. <br>It is interoperable and continuously integrates new technologies to support the digital transformation strategies of businesses, <br>public entities, and software developers.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"323\" height=\"156\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/telechargement-.webp\" alt=\"Managed Services​\" /></figure><h3>Managed Services</h3><p>With extensive experience in production management, we are your trusted partner for digital transformations. <br>Our human and technical resources ensure 24/7 operational maintenance of your information systems, state-of-the-art security, and cost-effective solutions aligned with your needs.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"348\" height=\"145\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Cybersecurity.webp\" alt=\"CyberSecruite cloud\" /></figure><h3>Cybersecurity</h3><p>Security is at the core of our expertise, model, and DNA. It permeates all our services, from cloud hosting to managed services. To provide our clients with the most innovative cybersecurity solutions, we continuously evolve our service offerings.</p>		\n			<h2>Leading team</h2>		\n		<p>OUR LEADERS</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/carlos-lindner-ZVo7vtXilCs-unsplash.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure><p>Support Staff</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/nate-johnston-R8IdNx4eJH0-unsplash.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h5>Alicia Anderson</h5><p>Support Staff</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/charles-etoroma-95UF6LXe-Lo-unsplash.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h5>Michael Clark</h5><p>Support Staff</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/otech/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/corinne-kutz-jfIgh0ijkqM-unsplash.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h5>Stacy Henderson</h5><p>Support Staff</p>		\n			collaborators			\n				0\n			Projects			\n				0\n			Missions			\n				0','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','965-r